  "The rate and amount are inversely related": "费率和数额有反比关系",
  "The rate equals a constant multiple of the current value: dy/dt = ky": "率等于当前值的常数倍数: dy/ dt = Ky",
  "Proportional means the relationship dy/dt = ky holds for some constant k (the proportionality constant). The rate of change is always a fixed fraction (k) of the current value y.": "比例表示关系 dy/dt = ky 持有某种恒定 k(相称性常数) 。 变化率始终是当前值y 的固定分数(k)。",
