  "What does 'asymptotic behavior' mean in exponential decay?": "\"无药可治的行为\"在指数衰变中意味着什么?",
  "The decaying quantity approaches zero (or the ambient value) but theoretically never exactly reaches it": "衰变的数量接近零(或环境值),但理论上从未完全达到",
