  "Set A(t) = 50: 50 = 200e^(-0.1t), 1/4 = e^(-0.1t), -0.1t = ln(1/4) = -ln(4), t = 10 ln(4) approximately 13.9 hours.": "A组(t) = 50: 50 = 200e(-0.1t), 1/4 = e(-0.1t), --0.1t = In(1/4) = -ln(4), t = 10 In(4) 大约13.9小时。",
  "A city's population was 50,000 in 2000 and 65,000 in 2010. Using the exponential growth model, predict the population in 2030.": "一个城市的人口2000年为50,000人,2010年为65,000人,使用指数增长模型预测2030年的人口。",
