  "100000e^(-1.2) dollars (approximately $30,119)": "100 000e(-1.2)美元(约30 119美元)",
  "A = Pe^(rt): 100000 = Pe^(0.06*20) = Pe^(1.2). So P = 100000e^(-1.2) approximately $30,119.": "A=Pe(t):100 000=Pe(0.06*20)=Pe(1.2)。P=100 000e(-1.2)约30 119美元。",
  "A lake with initial temperature 80 degrees F cools to 60 degrees F in autumn when the air temperature is 40 degrees F. If the cooling follows T(t) = 40 + 40e^(-kt) and T(30) = 60, find the time to reach 45 degrees F.": "当空气温度为40华氏度时,一个初始温度为80华氏度的湖泊在秋季冷却到60华氏度。 如果冷却跟随T(t) = 40+ 40e(-kt)和T(30) = 60,则找到时间达到45华氏度。",
  "45 days, based": "45天,基数",
  "30 * ln(8)/ln(2) = 90 days": "30 *in(8)ln(2)=90天",
  "60 days regardless": "60天,不论",
  "120 days under most": "最多120天以下",
  "T(30) = 60: 20 = 40e^(-30k), e^(-30k) = 1/2, k = ln(2)/30. T(t) = 45: 5 = 40e^(-kt), e^(-kt) = 1/8, kt = ln(8) = 3 ln(2), t = 3 ln(2)/k = 3 ln(2)/(ln(2)/30) = 90 days.": "T(30) = 60: 20 = 40e__(30k)、 e__(30k) = 1/2, k = In(2)/30.T(t) = 45: 5 = 40e__(-kt)、 e__(-kt) = 1/8、 kt = In(8) = 3 In(2), t = 3 In(2)/k = 3 In(2)/(ln(2)/30) = 90天。",
  "A museum displays a Strontium-90 sample (half-life 28.8 years). The sample currently has 40 grams. A safety regulation requires removal when less than 5 grams remain. In what year can the sample be removed if the current year is 2025?": "博物馆展示的是-90样本(半衰期为28.8年),目前样本有40克。安全条例规定,如果还剩下不到5克,则需要清除。如果当年是2025年,在哪一年可以清除样本?",
  "Year 2083 when considering all": "2083年,考虑所有",
  "2025 + 28.8 * 3 = approximately year 2111": "2025 + 28.8 * 3 = 大约2111年",
  "Year 2053, at least according": "2053年,至少根据",
  "Year 2200, even when conditions": "2200年,即使条件",
  "5 = 40(1/2)^(t/28.8), 1/8 = (1/2)^(t/28.8), (1/2)^3 = (1/2)^(t/28.8), so t/28.8 = 3, t = 86.4 years. Year = 2025 + 86.4 approximately 2111.": "5 = 40(1/2)(t/28.8),1/8 = (1/2)(t/28.8),1/2)3 = (1/2)(t/28.8), 所以 t/28.8 = 3, t = 86.4 岁,年 = 2025 + 86.4 约 2111。",
  "A bank offers two accounts: Account A at 5% compounded annually, and Account B at 4.9% compounded continuously. Which yields more after 10 years on a $10,000 deposit?": "银行提供两个账户:账户A每年5%的复数,账户B4.9%的复数,持续复数。 10年后,在10 000美元的存款上,谁能再多赚10 000美元?",
  "Account A yields more when viewed through a simplified analytical lens": "如果通过简化的分析透镜来看待一个账户,其产量就会增加",
  "Cannot be determined without more information regardless of prevailing conditions": "不论普遍条件如何,在不提供更多信息的情况下无法确定",
  "They yield the same amount, even when conditions shift significantly": "即使条件发生重大变化,它们也产生相同数额的收益",
  "Account A: 10000(1.05)^10 = $16,288.95 vs Account B: 10000e^(0.49) = $16,323.16; Account B wins": "账户A:10000(1.05)_10=16 288.95美元;账户B:10 000e_(0.49)=16 323.16美元;账户B赢",
  "Account A: 10000(1.05)^10 approximately $16,288.95. Account B: 10000e^(0.49) approximately $16,323.16. Account B (continuous compounding at 4.9%) slightly outperforms Account A (annual at 5%).": "账户A:10000(1.05)10约16 288.95美元。账户B:10000e(0.49)约16 323.16美元。账户B(连续复数为4.9%)略优于账户A(每年5%)。"
